body: "GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/446\n\n## Problem\n`pm get` omits the schedule facet (events/start_at/end_at/location) for Meeting/Event/Reminder items — the single-item read primitive cannot show the defining fields of calendar types; agents must fall back to calendar/agenda commands.\n\n## Proposed fix\nInclude the schedule facet in pm get output (standard depth and above; respect --fields), matching where list/agenda expose it.\n\n## Definition of done\npm get shows events/start_at/end_at/location for scheduled types in TOON and JSON; spec added; docs COMMANDS.md get section updated."
